{"id":282620,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/【图说天朝】大哭的孩子-被反绑的母亲/","date":"2013-03-07T03:49:29Z","modified":"2013-03-07T18:13:50Z","title":"【图说天朝】大哭的孩子 被反绑的母亲","content":"<p>3月6日15时40分，广州大道南靠近客村立交处，城管执法试图赶走一带着小孩的女小贩。双方发生口角后，突然一名制服编号X080324的城管执法人员上去掐住女小贩脖子意图将其放倒。随后，小贩老公到场，发现妻子被警方强行扣押上警车，要求城管下车给出说法，对方不予理睬。她的孩子在一旁放声大哭。冲突之后，女小贩的孩子惊恐地抱着她的妈妈。 （南都）</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-2' class='gallery galleryid-282620 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e5%a4%a7%e5%93%ad%e7%9a%84%e5%ad%a9%e5%ad%90-%e8%a2%ab%e5%8f%8d%e7%bb%91%e7%9a%84%e6%af%8d%e4%ba%b2/8pb946t200ap0001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/8PB946T200AP0001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-2-282621\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/8PB946T200AP0001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/8PB946T200AP0001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-2-282621'>\n\t\t\t\t城管与女小贩发生口角，一名制服编号X080324的城管执法人员掐着女小贩脖子意图将其按倒。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c